---
title: Quick Seared Pork & Creamy Garlic Sauce with Mash & Sautéed Veggies
description: We're not going to lie – this creamy garlic sauce is so good you'll want to slather it over everything! Here, we've teamed it with tender pork steaks, pan-fried veggies and potato mash, all ready in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-pork-potato-mash-030f3265.jpg
